title: Cool idea, but glitches
text:
I like the idea but mine seems to glitch really bad. Ivan never type anything more than 3 words on the app. I have to type it outside of the app ten copy and paste it into the text box or it will freeze on me. 

Other than that if I d the app to be very community based. The Algo also seems to be pretty good bc I get no annoying ads (yet) and all of the things that are popping up on my feed are pretty related to my interests. 

It’s fun so far. Wish they’d spend time bringing Instagram back up to par tho 🤣
